column1: ##### Please remove the sample and below descriptions when importing ############
Above lines are sample information for importing csv
The 1st column is action. It must be "ADD" "EDIT" "MOVE" or "DELETE".
The 2nd column is Device ID. Enter IMEI or Serial Number or MAC Address of device.
The 3rd column is Device Model and Carrier Code
The 4th column is Label. It is not necessary.
The 5th column is Friendly Name. It is not necessary.
